-19T13:20:46.000Z","msg":"我所知情情緒會影響腸胃消化問題。<br />\n<br />\n我本身有其他病而胃酸倒流約6-7年,轉過2隻藥無效最後食Dexilant60mg都唔得,每晚半夜3點就有胃酸湧上食道立即再食Famotidine2粒,假如無效再食喜胃斯康。 <br />\n<br />\n喜胃斯康對胃酸倒流好有功效,我大約食10次有2次止唔到胃酸上食道。<br />\n<br />\n我呢幾年照過3次胃鏡檢查,食道和胃都有輕微發炎 , 最後醫生提意做食道壓力測試,24小時胃酸監察和飲顯影劑照x光檢查食道,就確定100%係胃酸倒流 。<br />\n<br />\n轉頭有時間再打埋落去"},{"pid":"85d0d863696bcf9e1d8bc133578fe443b6b19faf","tid":668743,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T13:37:34.000Z","msg":"試下飲蘋果醋"},{"pid":"b5a1c6cb77eb9979882b544007daad56bf6e242a","tid":668743,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85d0d863696bcf9e1d8bc133578fe443b6b19faf","tid":668743,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T13:37:34.000Z","msg":"試下飲蘋果醋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T13:57:27.000Z","msg":"吓？酸性個喎，會唔會反效果？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a5baaa851a3e770748b21d4d68ad6fd02acf0f","tid":668743,"uid":50677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5a1c6cb77eb9979882b544007daad56bf6e242a","tid":668743,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85d0d863696bcf9e1d8bc133578fe443b6b19faf","tid":668743,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T13:37:34.000Z","msg":"試下飲蘋果醋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T13:57:27.000Z","msg":"吓？酸性個喎，會唔會反效果？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T15:17:42.000Z","msg":"我手術前半夜胃酸上食道,假如食藥唔得就飲維他奶都有少功效。<br />\n<br />\n同埋手術前我都有食野久唔久落錯格同感覺食物係食道唔上唔落。<br />\n做食道壓力測試醫生係儀器都見到有呢個情況。"},{"pid":"37ef0cf8d4277829c785a873a08c5f417ed64fa6","tid":668743,"uid":55011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a14fb94ae89c342ed04c6ce6e2d7bd0468b59f47","tid":668743,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab6492d6b1277ff969928a0c0242e13781615c82","tid":668743,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"293172adec0f8ac4160cd997abaa67cd